CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 9, 2006

[Cite as 05/09/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2256.]

*1452MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2005-2320. Cincinnati School Dist. Bd. of Edn. v. Hamilton Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2004-A-767. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
